Package com.nair.cache.expirable

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IExpirableCache<K,V>
    This is the Global interface for an Expirable Cache.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractExpirableCacheKey
    This class is the Abstract Expirable Cache Key, and contains all logic of when Key is to be expired.
    ExpirableCache<K,V>
    The storage engine for an Expirable Cache.
    ExpirableCacheCleaner<K,V>
    This Class is used for Clean Up of the Expirable Cache.
    ExpirableCacheKey<K>
    This class is the wrapper class for all keys stored in an ExpirableCache
    ExpirableCacheValue<K extends ExpirableCacheKey<?>,V>
    Used to wrap the values that are to be stored in an ExpirableCache
